Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[芙蓉 枫 篇 后篇]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚回来就又出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅她们好像也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要谈约会的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 衣服什么的就穿平时的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想单单只是和禀一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐就十分高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时总是禀和亚沙学姐还有我三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这一次是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日我答应要和莉姆一起去买洋服的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管怎样我也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不用做我的晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们整理一下院子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 出门之前我没说过不回来吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 抱歉 我马上收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息嘛 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去重新热一下酱汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我约了亚沙学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以不用准备饭菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 趁禀出去的这段时间 洗洗衣服扫扫地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚沙学姐在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为禀出去时显得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次 第一次看到那么幸福的禀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要禀幸福就什么都无所谓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要禀幸福 枫就什么都无所谓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾禀是我活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要禀幸福就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 是禀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我要在亚沙学姐家吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭我就不回来吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚麻小姐 这么多怎么吃的掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小禀还年轻嘛 再多也吃的下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就死心吧 味道我可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 就是这样 要晚些回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我来打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你回去 请回去 请回去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回去 回去 别进来这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把禀还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 你是怎么了 冷静一点 疯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人 给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 是芙蓉家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 我还在医院里 今天会很晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先把饭吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐她...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀也不要太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 怎么没去上课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...有点东西忘记带了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么禀要做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地步是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 又不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么禀要一直陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是怎么了 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然快了点 不过晚饭已经做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我肚子还不饿 你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么是要洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要躺一会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终都没怎么睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...亚沙学姐身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是已经没事了 明天就出院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐她啊 听说以前和亚麻小姐关系很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在关系却那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐她很后悔伤害了自己最珍重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚麻小姐也十分替学姐着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么呢 感觉像是心意在哪里错开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我 又有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀总是介意那些痛苦着的人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是不是也该更痛苦一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 喂 你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 求你了 别离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想永远照顾着禀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 别离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了禀 我什么都...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 等一下 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我一定是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 禀 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的 就只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要一直做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像现在这样 像现在这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的心愿就是禀得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要接受禀的所有心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他喜欢亚沙学姐也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要禀还留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会着凉的 我马上去热洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有什么不足之处 我可以改的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理的话 我也会学更多禀喜欢的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会越做越好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你别说要离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚沙学姐的事吗 那个的话 我完全不在意...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要能照顾禀就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为禀做饭 为禀洗衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的吧 枫只要这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的心意 我也对枫你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为禀效劳是我的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要禀才是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此我才要离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是不得不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 别离开 别从我眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是当然的 我对禀做过那么过份的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样还想照顾禀 为他效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了禀活着 这是我唯一的赎罪方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...我意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和禀在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是赎罪 其实却只是想呆在禀的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那一天的赎罪用来做这种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀没有选择我 而选择了亚沙学姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 这是禀自己的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么都会继续爱着禀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是注定不会被禀所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚沙学姐一起的话 禀一定会幸福的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请让我提一个任性的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看着 只从远处看着就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我继续喜欢禀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一直喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道禀喜欢的是亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而却...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢 淋成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和亚沙学姐谈了一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把禀拜托给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经不能照顾禀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 我对亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说了 事到如今不用再多告诉我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白了 我不想听禀亲口说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 对枫你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是对枫你 所以我必须说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了很多 我现在最需要的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在最想陪伴的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 我最爱的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫也是我很重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一起生活 一直陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都还要多注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能讨厌和我共度过比任何人的时光都多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是以恋人的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢枫你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我 喜欢 喜欢禀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 禀 禀


